OL,4,CGermany passes new citizenship law for
OL,5,Cdescendants of Nazi victims
OL,6, German lawmakers have approved changes
OL,7, that will make it easier for
OL,8, descendants of those who fled Nazi
OL,9, persecution to obtain citizenship.
OL,11,FUnder German law, people stripped of
OL,12,Ftheir citizenship on political, racial
OL,13,For religious grounds can have it
OL,14,Frestored, and so can their descendants.
OL,16,FBut legal loopholes had prevented many
OL,17,Fpeople from benefiting.
OL,19,FCampaigners say the move allow many to
OL,20,Freconnect with their German heritage,
OL,21,Fparticularly in the Jewish community.
